115
00:09:31,078 --> 00:09:33,893
Apa yang harus kulakukan?

116
00:09:35,318 --> 00:09:37,523
Jika nilaimu kurang, dia akan membunuhmu

117
00:09:39,519 --> 00:09:40,693
